insert into dim_isp_time SELECT to_number(to_char(ADD_MONTHS(date_from,(LEVEL-1)),'YYYY')|| to_char(ADD_MONTHS(date_from,(LEVEL-1)),'Q') || to_char(ADD_MONTHS(date_from,(LEVEL-1)),'MM')) id , to_number(to_char(ADD_MONTHS(date_from,(LEVEL-1)),'YYYY') || to_char(ADD_MONTHS(date_from,(LEVEL-1)),'MM')) id_without_quarter, ADD_MONTHS(date_from,(LEVEL-1)) begin_date, lAST_DAY(ADD_MONTHS(date_from,(LEVEL-1))) end_date, to_char(ADD_MONTHS(date_from,(LEVEL-1)),'MON') MONTH, to_char(ADD_MONTHS(date_from,(LEVEL-1)),'YYYY') || '/' || to_char(ADD_MONTHS(date_from,(LEVEL-1)),'MON') MONTH_ID, to_number(to_char(ADD_MONTHS(date_from,(LEVEL-1)),'YYYY') || to_char(ADD_MONTHS(date_from,(LEVEL-1)),'MM')) MONTH_INT
FROM (SELECT from_dt date_from ,to_dt date_to ,MONTHS_BETWEEN (to_dt,from_dt) days_between FROM (SELECT to_date( #ETLFORSELECTEDPROVIDER.DDO_START_MON_YYYY,'MON-YYYY') from_dt , to_date((select to_char(add_months((select sysdate from dual),1),'mon-yyyy') from dual),'MON-YYYY') to_dt FROM dual)) CONNECT BY (LEVEL-1) <= days_between
